subSubSection.paragraph:
Biology.
In 
Japan
, adults were observed in October, November, and March (the present study). Conversely, adults were collected from September to February in other distribution areas (
Drake & Ruhoff 1965b
; 
Péricart 1985a
; 
Guilbert 2015
).
